enced position, with redshirt senior Keith
Blass, redshirt sophomore Toure Weaver,
and sophomore Miles Dowiak as the top
returnees. ,

One of the new additions to the team
is redshirt‘ junior Chris Churchill, who
transferred to Pitt from cross,-state rival
Penn State. '

The team’s only freshman, Clay

‘Haﬂich, will also be a member of the

defense corps, and "should contribute
immediately.
The starting goalkeeper position was

one that had no question marks attached as
the preseason drew to a close. Sophomore
Justin Gaul returns after starting all 19
games as a true freshman last year. He

posted a 1.10 goals against average and p

six shutouts.
